License: ZPL 2.1
Description: *******
        zc.rst2
        *******
        
        Script for converting from reStructuredText to various formats.
        
        Usage: rst2 writer [arguments]
        
        The first argument is tha name of a docutils "writer".
        
        Changes
        *******
        
        0.2 (2006-02-04)
        ================
        
        Added support for loading custom reStructuredText directives from
        rst.directive entry points.
        
Keywords: reStructutedText
